description: Demolition of all existing buildings & redevelopment of site by the erection of a part four storey building on Cable Street frontage and part seven storey building on Schoolhouse Lane frontage (including basement) for mixed use purposes comprising 4430 sqm commercial B1 floor space (of which 2650sqm will be retained by T. W. Ides Paragon Ltd ), 220 sqm. retail floor space, 211 residential units inclusive of basement/ground floor parking for 121 cars. (Please note the revisions consist of reduction of residential units from 238 to 211 plus amendments to the design of the courtyard and creation of disabled car parking bays.) This application is a revision of the application that included the submission of an Environmental Statement under the provisions of the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 1999.
